{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1229,"text":"The digital divide is a mother\nthat's 45 years old and can't get a job,"},{"time":5689,"text":"because she doesn't know\nhow to use a computer."},{"time":7919,"text":"It is an immigrant that doesn't know\nthat he can call his family for free."},{"time":11651,"text":"It is a child who can't\nresolve his homework,"},{"time":14813,"text":"because he doesn't have\naccess to information."},{"time":17041,"text":"The digital divide is a new illiteracy."},{"time":19852,"text":"\"Digital divide\" is also defined as:"},{"time":21738,"text":"the gap between individuals\nand communities"},{"time":23822,"text":"that have access\nto information technologies"},{"time":25964,"text":"and those that don't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27141,"text":"Why does this happen?\nIt happens because of 3 things."},{"time":29703,"text":"The first is that people can't get\naccess to these technologies"},{"time":33171,"text":"because they can't afford them."},{"time":34718,"text":"The second is because\nthey don't know how to use them."},{"time":37326,"text":"The third is because they don't know\nthe benefits derived from technology."},{"time":40937,"text":"So let's consider\nsome very basic statistics."},{"time":44677,"text":"The population of the world\nis nearly seven billion people."},{"time":48122,"text":"Out of these, approximately two billion\nare digitally included."},{"time":51958,"text":"This is approximately 30%\nof the entire world population,"},{"time":55474,"text":"which means that the remaining\n70% of the world --"},{"time":60346,"text":"close to five billion people --"},{"time":62997,"text":"do not have access\nto a computer or the internet."},{"time":65477,"text":"Let's think about\nthat number for a second."},{"time":67569,"text":"Five billion people; that's four\ntimes the population of India,"},{"time":72080,"text":"that have never touched a computer,\nhave never accessed the internet."},{"time":75607,"text":"So this is a digital abyss\nthat we're talking about,"},{"time":78140,"text":"this is not a digital divide."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79763,"text":"Here we can see a map by Chris Harrison"},{"time":81977,"text":"that shows the internet connections\naround the world."},{"time":84525,"text":"What we can see is that most\nof the internet connections"},{"time":87273,"text":"are centered on North America and Europe,"},{"time":89296,"text":"while the rest of the world is engulfed\nin the dark shadow of digital divide."},{"time":93757,"text":"Next, we can see connections,\ncity-to-city, around the world,"},{"time":97377,"text":"and we can see that most\nof the information generated"},{"time":99942,"text":"is being generated\nbetween North America and Europe,"},{"time":103211,"text":"while the rest of the world is not\nbroadcasting their ideas or information."},{"time":106982,"text":"So what does this mean?"},{"time":109237,"text":"We are living in a world that seems\nto be having a digital revolution,"},{"time":114347,"text":"a revolution that everyone here\nthinks that we're part of,"},{"time":118407,"text":"but the 70% of the world that is\ndigitally excluded is not part of this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":122186,"text":"What does this mean?"},{"time":123377,"text":"Well, the people that will be digitally\nexcluded won't be able to compete"},{"time":127525,"text":"in the labor markets of the future,"},{"time":129423,"text":"they won't be connected,\nthey'll be less informed,"},{"time":131871,"text":"they'll be less inspired"},{"time":133134,"text":"and they'll be less responsible."},{"time":134792,"text":"Internet should not be a luxury,\nit should be a right,"},{"time":137687,"text":"because it is a basic social necessity\nof the 21st century."},{"time":141301,"text":"We can't operate without it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":142738,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":145020,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146297,"text":"It allows us to connect to the world."},{"time":149031,"text":"It empowers us."},{"time":150220,"text":"It gives us social participation.\nIt is a tool for change."},{"time":155571,"text":"And so, how are we going\nto bridge this digital divide?"},{"time":159286,"text":"Well, there are many models\nthat try and bridge the digital divide,"},{"time":163333,"text":"that try and include\nthe population at large."},{"time":166348,"text":"But the question is:\nAre they really working?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":169764,"text":"I'm sure everybody here\nknows One Laptop per Child,"},{"time":172403,"text":"where one computer is given to one child."},{"time":175951,"text":"The problem with this is,"},{"time":177282,"text":"do we really want children\nto take computers to their homes,"},{"time":180384,"text":"homes that have adverse conditions?"},{"time":182574,"text":"And we also must understand\nthat by giving a child a computer,"},{"time":185546,"text":"we're also transferring costs,\nvery high costs,"},{"time":188205,"text":"such as internet connection, electricity,\nmaintenance, software, updates."},{"time":194037,"text":"So we must create different models,"},{"time":195850,"text":"models that help the families\nrather than add a burden on them."},{"time":200816,"text":"Also, let's not forget\nabout the carbon footprint."},{"time":203960,"text":"Imagine five billion laptops."},{"time":206254,"text":"What would the world look like then?"},{"time":208086,"text":"Imagine the hazardous residue\nthat would be generated from that."},{"time":211198,"text":"Imagine the trash."},{"time":212450,"text":"So if we give one computer to one person,"},{"time":216840,"text":"and we multiply that times five billion,"},{"time":220767,"text":"even if that laptop is a hundred dollars,"},{"time":222871,"text":"then we would have 483 trillion dollars."},{"time":226684,"text":"Now let's consider we're only counting\nthe youth, ages 10 to 24."},{"time":231851,"text":"That's approximately 30%\nof the digitally excluded population."},{"time":235180,"text":"Then that would be 145 trillion dollars."},{"time":237537,"text":"What nation has this amount of money?"},{"time":240248,"text":"This is not a sustainable model."}]},{"cues":[{"time":242335,"text":"So with this in mind,\nwe created a different model."},{"time":244917,"text":"We created the RIA, in Spanish,"},{"time":247600,"text":"or in English, Learning\nand Innovation Network,"},{"time":249957,"text":"which is a network of community centers"},{"time":252196,"text":"that bring education\nthrough the use of technology."},{"time":254637,"text":"We wanted to increase the number\nof users per computer in such a way"},{"time":257954,"text":"that we could dilute the cost\nof infrastructure, the cost per user,"},{"time":261394,"text":"and that we could bring\neducation and technology"},{"time":263850,"text":"to everybody within these communities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":266392,"text":"Let's look at a basic comparison."},{"time":269412,"text":"The RIA has 1,650 computers."},{"time":272918,"text":"If we had used\nthe One Laptop per Child model"},{"time":275439,"text":"of a 1 to 1 ratio,"},{"time":276696,"text":"then we would have benefited 1,650 users."},{"time":280861,"text":"What we did instead is set up centers"},{"time":283527,"text":"that have longer hours\nof operation than schools,"},{"time":286965,"text":"that also include all of the population --"},{"time":289454,"text":"our youngest user is 3 years old,\nthe oldest is 86 --"},{"time":293094,"text":"and with this, in less than two years,\nwe were able to reach 140,000 users,"},{"time":299948,"text":"out of which --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":301186,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":302609,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304333,"text":"out of which, 34,000 have already\ngraduated from our courses."}]},{"cues":[{"time":308336,"text":"Another thing with One Laptop per Child\nis that it doesn't guarantee"},{"time":311630,"text":"the educational use of a computer."},{"time":313318,"text":"Technology is nothing\nwithout that content."},{"time":315944,"text":"We need to use it\nas a means, not as an end."},{"time":319274,"text":"How did we accomplish such a high impact?"},{"time":324050,"text":"Well, you can't just go into a community\nand pretend to change it,"},{"time":327311,"text":"you need to look at a lot of factors."},{"time":329134,"text":"So what we do is a thing\nwe call \"urban acupuncture.\""},{"time":332091,"text":"We first start by looking\nat the basic geography of a site."},{"time":335816,"text":"So take, for example, Ecatepec."},{"time":337394,"text":"This is one of the most densely\npopulated municipalities in Mexico."},{"time":342052,"text":"It has a very low income level."},{"time":345175,"text":"So we look at the basic geography,\nwe look at roads, streets,"},{"time":348699,"text":"the flux of pedestrians and vehicles."},{"time":351317,"text":"Then we look at income,\nwe look at education."},{"time":353797,"text":"Then we set up a center there"},{"time":357041,"text":"in the place that's going\nto heal the body,"},{"time":359490,"text":"a little needle to change the city body."},{"time":364180,"text":"And there we go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":365356,"text":"And so, there are four basic elements\nthat we need to consider"},{"time":368395,"text":"when we're using education\nthrough technology."},{"time":372413,"text":"The first one is we need to create spaces."},{"time":375341,"text":"We need to create a space\nthat is welcoming to the community,"},{"time":378853,"text":"a space that is according to the needs\nof the children and of the elders"},{"time":384179,"text":"and of every possible person\nthat lives within that community."},{"time":388801,"text":"So we create these spaces\nthat are all made with recycled materials."},{"time":392384,"text":"We use modular architecture\nto lower the ecological impact."}]},{"cues":[{"time":397804,"text":"And second, connection."},{"time":401943,"text":"By connection, I mean not only\na connection to the internet,"},{"time":404920,"text":"that's too easy."},{"time":406120,"text":"We need to create a connection\nthat's an interconnection of humans."},{"time":409717,"text":"The internet is a very complex organism"},{"time":414258,"text":"that is fueled of the ideas, the thoughts\nand the emotions of human beings."},{"time":418842,"text":"We need to create networks\nthat aid in exchanging information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":423000,"text":"Third, content."},{"time":425033,"text":"Education is nothing without content."},{"time":427344,"text":"And you can't pretend\nto have a relationship"},{"time":429631,"text":"of only a computer with a child."},{"time":431423,"text":"So we create a route,\na very basic learning route,"},{"time":436909,"text":"where we teach people\nhow to use a computer,"},{"time":439002,"text":"how to use the internet,\nhow to use office software,"},{"time":441687,"text":"and in 72 hours,\nwe create digital citizens."},{"time":445106,"text":"You can't pretend that people\nare just going to touch a computer"},{"time":448229,"text":"and become digitally included,"},{"time":449701,"text":"you need to have a process."},{"time":451054,"text":"And after this, then they can take on\na longer educational route."}]},{"cues":[{"time":454816,"text":"And then fourth, training."},{"time":458209,"text":"We need to train not only the users,"},{"time":461194,"text":"but we need to train the people\nthat will facilitate learning"},{"time":464195,"text":"for these people."},{"time":465401,"text":"When you're talking about\nthe digital divide,"},{"time":467698,"text":"people have stigmas, people have fears;"},{"time":469603,"text":"people don't understand how\nit can complement their lives."},{"time":472558,"text":"So what we do is train facilitators"},{"time":474302,"text":"so that they can help\nin breaking that digital barrier."}]},{"cues":[{"time":479483,"text":"So, we have four elements:"},{"time":481425,"text":"we have a space that's created,"},{"time":483987,"text":"we have a connection,"},{"time":485324,"text":"we have content and we have training."},{"time":487341,"text":"We have created\na digital learning community."},{"time":489732,"text":"But there is one more element,"},{"time":491720,"text":"which is the benefits\nthat technology can create,"},{"time":496618,"text":"because it is not printed, static content."},{"time":498738,"text":"It is dynamic; it is modifiable."},{"time":501040,"text":"So we have we do is, we provide\ncontent, then we do training,"},{"time":505638,"text":"then we analyze the user patterns\nso that we can improve content."},{"time":509237,"text":"So it creates a virtuous circle."},{"time":510861,"text":"It allows us to deliver education"},{"time":512490,"text":"according to different\ntypes of intelligence"},{"time":514652,"text":"and according to different user needs."},{"time":516990,"text":"With this in mind,"},{"time":519169,"text":"we have to think that technology\nis something that can modify"},{"time":524816,"text":"according to human processes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":526888,"text":"I want to share a story."},{"time":528103,"text":"In 2006, I went to live here."},{"time":530192,"text":"This is one of the poorest\ncommunities in all of Mexico."},{"time":534154,"text":"I went to film a documentary\non the people that live off trash,"},{"time":537288,"text":"entirely of trash -- their houses\nare built with trash,"},{"time":539945,"text":"they eat trash, they dress in trash."},{"time":541776,"text":"And after two months of living with them,"},{"time":543847,"text":"of seeing the children\nand the way they work,"},{"time":546053,"text":"I understood that the only thing\nthat can change"},{"time":549119,"text":"and that can break the poverty\ncycle is education."},{"time":552546,"text":"And we can use technology\nto bring education to these communities."},{"time":557378,"text":"Here is another shot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":559216,"text":"The main message is that technology\nis not going to save the world;"},{"time":565697,"text":"we are, and we can use\ntechnology to help us."},{"time":569692,"text":"I'm sure everybody here\nhas experienced it;"},{"time":572302,"text":"what moves technology is human energy."},{"time":574377,"text":"So let's use this energy\nto make the world a better place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":577738,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":578921,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}